title: Praise/Worship Music
description:
<!--StartFragment-->

This well-known type of music is used widely in church services. This style is dedicated to beautifully arranged musical themes and lyrics that help us focus on God as we sing to Him. Most praise music today uses drums, electric guitars and acoustic guitars with some piano too.

<!--EndFragment-->
